name: Add cello tuning
body:
* Add cello tuning
* Set chromatic tuning as the default
* Fix scrolling issue with tuning drop-down list in landscape mode

name: Remember last selected tuning when app is closed

body: The sampling rate has been reduced to increase sensitivity. The deviation is being rounded to the nearest mark on the gauge to counteract erratic pointer movements which would otherwise occur when displaying precise values with increased sensitivity.
Add support for different tunings (standard guitar and ukulele tuning as well as Drop D guitar tuning)
